FT  19 MAY 92 / Parliament and Politics: Rise in number of DTI probes
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
COMMERCIAL investigation requests made to the Department of Trade and
Industry rose sharply in the fiscal year ended March 31 to 811, up from 723
